column5: I got up north of sudbury with some friends to do some walleye and pike fishing.  Fishing was great.Caught everything on jigs and gulp minnows in deep water, 30 feet of water.       [
A few good eating size walleye there - thanks for sharing!  What happened to the line in picture 2?  It looks kind of like a noose on that poor pickeral.
Looks like a good time was had - nice fish!
